{"tid":702569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英人呼籲攻擊伊斯蘭教徒被控","createTime":"2018-06-15T04:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T04:24:08.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b703c8d9a2bd1b5dff2a714b404d943794ddd6df","tid":702569,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"英國一名男子涉嫌寄匿名信，呼籲大眾攻擊伊斯蘭教徒，被控教唆謀殺等十四項罪名。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦等多個地區的民眾三月起陸續收到匿名信件，提到四月三日是「懲罰穆斯林」的日子，呼籲大眾攻擊伊斯蘭教徒，信中並指會根據攻擊程度來給予不同的獎勵。反恐警察於星期二拘捕35 歲的疑犯帕哈姆，並控告帕哈姆教唆謀殺及寄恐嚇信等多項罪名，案件星期五提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/528997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F528997&d=pJmRmfFXVjkpliUNsRgPq%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a8597533\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F528997&h=379b6762\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/528997</a>"},{"pid":"9162082f3a722936f52a176e23ab53124a09a10f","tid":702569,"uid":82450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"魔女狩獵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}